data.title: The James Franklin Group, LLC
data.text:
The James Franklin Group, LLC is a professional development services firm founded by Michelle D. Thomas and her husband, James D. Thomas in May, 2014.

The James Franklin Group, LLC is named in honor of Jim's father - James Franklin Thomas - who passed away in 2005.

Copyright Â© The James Franklin Group, LLC. All rights reserved.

Welcome to the James Franklin Group, LLC, a business dedicated to empowering professional women to be confident, dynamic, focused and driven leaders. Through customized development plans and meaningful one-on-one interactions, professionals will transform passion into a plan of action. Dr. Thomas provides her professional services nationwide.
